{"tid":2020663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列媒體指中國大使杜偉於睡夢中自然死亡 中國暫時未有回應","createTime":"2020-05-17T08:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T08:44:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcb5f8264527b2697ef4719bf79fd946c1bac4a","tid":2020663,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"以色列媒體指中國大使杜偉於睡夢中自然死亡<br />\n17.05.2020 16:30<br />\n<br />\n中國駐以色列大使杜偉，今早被發現在特拉維夫市郊官邸內的床上死亡，終年58歲。當地傳媒最先報道死訊，以色列外交部其後證實報道，暫時未知杜偉的死因，警方已展開調查。當地電視台引述急救人員指，初步跡象顯示杜偉是在睡夢中自然死亡。中國駐以色列大使館暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n杜偉在2016年起出任駐烏克蘭大使，今年2月獲任命，轉任以色列大使，到3月履新，他與妻子育有一名兒子，兩人目前都不在以色列。杜偉最近一次露面是上星期二，他與以色列外交部官員進行視像會議，雙方就進一步加強兩國在國際多邊領域溝通，及其他共同關心的問題交換意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288063&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288063%26csid%3D261_341&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2FUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=d6d97bbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288063&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"a5e549bc597bed55cc14ce112d21782eadd7762f","tid":2020663,"uid":53003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"以：無可疑"},{"pid":"e59db98b3cdcf7acf3432cd0c51b2cd60d326c78","tid":2020663,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5e549bc597bed55cc14ce112d21782eadd7762f","tid":2020663,"uid":53003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"以：無可疑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac79c7a2386a93d9f85219b567feca33971dcde","tid":2020663,"uid":342786,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:39:59.000Z","msg":"以色列 大使 自然死亡<br />\n聽到呢d keyword個腦自動有陰謀論彈出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f5ba748af6c4d1658f9bc7301eeca1ee5cdeea","tid":2020663,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"駐以色列 <br />\n支那大使<br />\n自然死亡<br />\n<br />\n一定冇可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1801f10c65f95e4c8a28c5be56c4ac432216828","tid":2020663,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"中左支那肺炎嗰啲支那狗死嗰一刻都係自然死亡架啦<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得唔計啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n共狗黨 : 「牠經不起病的考驗 , 憑甚麼要計算在死亡個案數字內 ? 」<br />\n支那狗 : 「汪汪 ~ 」"},{"pid":"af32c1418150793e7c7ab1f17b4515196867a22e","tid":2020663,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"爭取真初選 最後今天！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2020626\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2020626</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}